<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>لَا ينفذ حكمه لكل مِنْهُم<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p61"></span>على الصَّحِيح<a href="#p61" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p62"></span>وَمُقَابِله ينفذ حكمه لَهُم بِالْبَيِّنَةِ<a href="#p62" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
